{
  "texts": [
    "In addition, we test the interdependency between the independent variables skill category and educational level.",
    "The ANOVA shows that the variables are significantly reinforcing each other (F(2, 202) = 6.49, p < 0.01).",
    "Figure 3 shows that the scientific skills for Bachelor level questions are rated even higher than we would expect from considering the dependency of the rating on skill category and educational level individually.",
    "We also analyze the influence of the faculty on the assessment rating.",
    "Here, we do not find a significant influence (F(4, 101) = 0.79, p = 0.53)."
  ]
}